Borrowers aren't meant to be seen.

346
00:59:54,794 --> 00:59:56,091
Borrowers?

347
00:59:56,562 --> 00:59:58,587
We borrow from humans.

348
00:59:58,898 --> 01:00:01,196
Things we need.
Things they won't miss.

349
01:00:02,168 --> 01:00:05,604
Soap and cookies and sugar.
Electricity and gas, too.

350
